{"tid":2187514,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被追問法號  陳慧嫻剷青Look似師姑","createTime":"2020-09-03T16:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T19:02:26.000Z","uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"87d319f17578bbea5c84d22b778a7fad6f666ee4","tid":2187514,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2740000/2742540/20200903JLA013__20200903_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2740000%2F2742540%2F20200903JLA013__20200903_L.jpg&h=4625881e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被追問法號 陳慧嫻剷青Look似尼姑<br />\n發佈時間: 2020/09/03<br />\n<br />\n陳慧嫻近年長駐內地賺「人仔」，較少在香港公開現身，不過她十分愛錫粉絲，經常更新社交平台跟粉絲報告近況。昨日，慧嫻在社交網貼出一張自拍照，剪了新髮型的她留言︰「昨天去了剪頭髮！大師Billy哥哥就問我，陳小姐我可以點幫你呢？我劈頭第一句就話，你上次幫我剪得唔夠短呀，一個月咋，我又要返嚟再剪過！」言猶在耳，慧嫻形容自己的頭髮在電光火石之間已經唔見晒，她更笑指︰「鏟得咁青似乎都係第一次，我諗如果有日我決定做尼姑，個樣都應該唔會太差嘅&hellip;&hellip;好彩唔使見人住，下次講嘢都係要有所保留好啲。」有網民搞笑留言問慧嫻「師傅，請問法號？」亦有網民指她的髮型「好型仔」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2742540/被追問法號%20陳慧嫻剷青Look似尼姑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2742540%2F%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%BD%E5%95%8F%E6%B3%95%E8%99%9F%2520%E9%99%B3%E6%85%A7%E5%AB%BB%E5%89%B7%E9%9D%92Look%E4%BC%BC%E5%B0%BC%E5%A7%91&d=Cu9ZF5gMYzm72cT69JSRjQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=c5981c34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2742540/被追問法號%20陳慧嫻剷青Look似尼姑</a><br />\n<br />\n好柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a17fbefc45e71239ae799f30996c806fe1fdeff","tid":2187514,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:05:51.000Z","msg":"夜麻麻 薑巴唔好嚇人<br />\n好難訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c